            "id": 6391196,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 埃森哲(ACN-US)大漲5.06%，報205.03美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>埃森哲(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ACN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ACN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ACN-US</a>)截至台北時間20日03:06股價上漲9.88美元，報205.03美元，漲幅5.06%，成交量7,445,586（股），盤中最高價207.98美元、最低價187.00美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.02%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.13%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.04%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.15%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>埃森哲(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ACN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ACN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ACN-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-3.14%</li> <li>近 1 月：-12.73%</li> <li>近 3 月：-27.71%</li> <li>近 6 月：-18.53%</li> <li>今年以來：-27.26%</li></ul></section></main>",
